{"data":[{"date":"09:33 08/07","title":"Liverpool kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Fekir","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/liverpool-khong-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-fekir.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool mua Nabil Fekir th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Lyon, Jean-Michel Aulas kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Fekir</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Nabil Fekir l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool mua Nabil Fekir kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool mua Nabil Fekir kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/liverpool-khong-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-fekir.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Fekir l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Lyon. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ghi t\u1edbi 18 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Ligue 1, ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap anh c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNabil Fekir r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf c\u00e1nh, ch\u01a1i h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 trung phong c\u1eafm. HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Anfield. Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Fekir, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Liverpool th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-gay-soc-vu-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-liverpool-172-190006.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Fekir</span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Martial, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lyon kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Fekir cho Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool mua Nabil Fekir th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Lyon, Jean-Michel Aulas kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nabil Fekir\" title=\"Nabil Fekir\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/25/liverpool-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-tuyen-phap-len-60-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lyon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Nabil Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Fekir s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Lyon, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Fekir h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Lyon, t\u00f4i tin c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cFekir l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi, vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4046","checkdouble":"190670"},{"date":"09:55 08/07","title":"\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca h\u00fat kh\u00e1ch Premier League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/everton-va-tottenham-muon-mua-mina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham v\u00e0 Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barcelona. H\u1ecd r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Colombia.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mina t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u00ean \u0110T Colombia, Yerry Mina \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Anh h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Davinson Sanchez th\u00e0nh c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb v\u1edbi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 22 v\u00e0 23 tu\u1ed5i, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e2u d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Colombia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi ri\u00eang Mina, anh c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Colombia. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Barcelona \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p t\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai trong \u0111\u1ed9i. Khi b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf cao 1m95 c\u1ee7a Mina l\u00e0 v\u0169 kh\u00ed l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Colombia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham v\u00e0 Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barcelona h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tottenham v\u00e0 Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barcelona h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Tottenham-va-Everton-muon-mua-Yerry-Mina-cua-Barcelona-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mina l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Colombia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Mina m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Colombia tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan, ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Senegal. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Mina l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Anh \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, gi\u00fap Los Cafeteros \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5. D\u00f9 Colombia sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1eaft kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean TTCN</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nYerry Mina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca t\u1eadu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Palmeiras \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018. Nh\u01b0ng sau m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a 2017/18, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n ng\u1ea5y anh. Mina t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca h\u00fat kh\u00e1ch Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca h\u00fat kh\u00e1ch Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Hang-thai-Barca-hut-khach-Premier-League-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tottenham v\u00e0 Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Yerry Mina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec th\u1ebf, Barca t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea9y Mina ngay trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c g\u00ec khi trung v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u201chot\u201d tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau World Cup 2018 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, t\u1edd The Sun ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Tottenham v\u00e0 Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Yerry Mina. Tottenham c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft Davinson Sanchez v\u00e0 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Mina h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp r\u1ea5t nhanh v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Everton l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea1i Barca l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Mina kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Samuel Umtiti v\u00e0 Gerard Pique. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 4 \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Blaugrana mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Clement Lenglet t\u1eeb Sevilla.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/day-4-muc-tieu-sieu-khung-duoc-barca-nham-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-180-190595.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! 4 M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca nh\u1eafm n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-gui-loi-de-nghi-thu-2-mua-sao-chelsea-180-190491.html\">Barca g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 2 mua sao Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/messi-muon-barca-mua-ban-hop-dong-dat-gia-nhat-lich-su-mu-172-190483.html\">Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-tiep-tuc-nhan-don-dau-tren-ttcn-180-190407.html\">Barca ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au tr\u00ean TTCN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/willian-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-truoc-tin-don-duoc-barca-quan-tam-421-190386.html\">Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca quan t\u00e2m</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4045","checkdouble":"190671"},{"date":"10:15 08/07","title":"Liverpool ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u0103n sao tr\u1ebb h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/liverpool-van-muon-mua-grealish.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. H\u1ecd quy\u1ebft s\u1edf h\u1eefu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Tottenham c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Aston Villa bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n Grealish</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2017/18, Aston Villa gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh. H\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1 play-off, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Middlesbrough \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Fulham song sau c\u00f9ng thua 0-1. Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Premier League khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Birmingham \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Tony Xia ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Aston Villa s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n \u0111i c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c t\u1edbi tai nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i Premier League, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Jack Grealish.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/liverpool-van-muon-mua-grealish.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tottenham chi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho sao tr\u1ebb 22 tu\u1ed5i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBan \u0111\u1ea7u, Aston Villa ra gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Grealish. Nh\u01b0ng sau khi l\u1ed9 chuy\u1ec7n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i gi\u1ea3m xu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua c\u00f9ng Tottenham</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch 2017/18, Grealish l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh nh\u01b0 Tottenham hay Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTottenham s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Grealish. Ph\u00eda Aston Villa hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i cho \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c v\u00ec mu\u1ed1n ch\u1edd nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Grealish\" title=\"Jack Grealish\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/9/7/hlv-hodgson-giuc-sao-tre-aston-villa-som-chon-dtqg.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Liverpool v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn nay, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp v\u1eabn \u00e1n binh b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, theo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Mirror, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng Liverpool b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c. H\u1ecd \u00e2m th\u1ea7m theo s\u00e1t Grealish v\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh n\u1eb1m \u1edf vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua kim ti\u1ec1n v\u1edbi Tottenham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi chia tay Philippe Coutinho, hi\u1ec7n Liverpool v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thay th\u1ebf. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 ba Mohamed Salah, Sadio Mane v\u00e0 Roberto Firmino, HLV Klopp v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-klopp-muon-liverpool-mua-xherdan-shaqiri-172-190490.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Klopp mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Xherdan Shaqiri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-va-arsenal-khong-nen-chieu-mo-forsberg-172-190458.html\">Forsberg ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fabinho-khang-dinh-chua-tung-tien-gan-mu-172-190409.html\">Fabinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ee5t v\u1edbi MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-len-tieng-choc-tuc-man-utd-172-190403.html\">T\u00e2n binh Liverpool l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ecdc t\u1ee9c Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league-172-190387.html\">Sao sa c\u01a1 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4044","checkdouble":"190672"},{"date":"10:56 08/07","title":"Sadio Mane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/28/sadio-mane-noi-gi-khi-duoc-real-madrid-quan-tam.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sadio Mane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Liverpool v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m Mane</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a tin <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-muon-giai-cuu-david-luiz-172-189742.html\" target=\"_blank\">Los\u00a0Blancos quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mane</span> c\u1ee7a Liverpool.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sadio Mane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sadio Mane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/Sadio-Mane-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real quan t\u00e2m Mane\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Mane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u0169i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Liverpool, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Firmino v\u00e0 Salah h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 20 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 8 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 Champions League.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, anh c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1eafc b\u00e9n. Liverpool ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, song Real hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Los Blancos nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 Liverpool b\u1ecf ra 33 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Mane t\u1eeb Southampton, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Real d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a ra g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed m\u00e0 h\u1ecd b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mane t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sadio Mane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Liverpool v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp noi ve Mane\" title=\"Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Mane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/28/sadio-mane-noi-gi-khi-duoc-real-madrid-quan-tam.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mane h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u00f4ng tin Real quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ph\u00eda h\u1ecd. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Liverpool v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf M\u1ef9. Real l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u1edf Liverpool.\"</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Klopp l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV gi\u1ecfi, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4043","checkdouble":"190673"},{"date":"11:12 08/07","title":"David Luiz l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/5/27/david-luiz-len-tieng-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Luiz \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 David Luiz g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec cho Chelsea c\u1ea3. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1987 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady anh c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Conte.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/7/David-Luiz-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>David Luiz \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh David Luiz s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin Luiz c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-tu-choi-ban-david-luiz-voi-gia-17-trieu-bang-172-188530.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal quan t\u00e2m David Luiz</span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Porto v\u00e0 Napoli c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 David Luiz ra \u0111i. N\u1ebfu The Blues nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>David Luiz kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/Napoli-muon-mua-David-Luiz-cua-Chelsea-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>David Luiz kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i nghe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin \u0111\u1ed3n Porto mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 t\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Benfica v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi h\u1ecd\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Chelsea, t\u00f4i c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge \u1edf\u00a0m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a David Luiz, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Chelsea. V\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 cao \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf Stamford Bridge, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do r\u1eddi n\u01a1i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4042","checkdouble":"190674"},{"date":"07:36 08/07","title":"B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: Man Utd \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/8/ban-ket-world-cup-2018-man-utd-dung-thu-hai-ve-so-cau-thu-gop-mat.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh m\u00e0 n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 \u0111ang th\u1eafng l\u1edbn khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n 50 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf c\u00e1c c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 \u1edf Premier League.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh th\u1eafng th\u1ebf<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 92 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c b\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 41 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League (chi\u1ebfm t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 44.56%). Con s\u1ed1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Du am Anh vs Thuy Dien\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/ban-ket-world-cup-2018-man-utd-dung-thu-hai-ve-so-cau-thu-gop-mat.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 41 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Anh g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9ng sau Anh l\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p (Ligue 1) v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (La Liga) v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng 12 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. C\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c, Italia (7), B\u1ec9, Trung Qu\u1ed1c, Croatia (2), Scotland, \u00c1o, Nga, Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 v\u00e0 Ukraine (1).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong n\u01b0\u1edbc (Ligue 1 - t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 39.1%) v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Anh, chi\u1ebfm 21.7%. Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Croatia c\u00f2n th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 12 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh. Croatia c\u00f3 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1i Anh l\u00e0 Dejan Lovren (Liverpool).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ea5t<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 41 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Anh g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi c\u00e1c CLB \u1edf Premier League s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong nh\u00f3m n\u00e0y nh\u1ea5t. D\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 Tottenham v\u1edbi 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed3m Harry Kane, Dele Alli, Eric Dier, Trippier, Danny Rose (Anh), Alderweireld, Vertonghen, Mousa Dembele (B\u1ec9), Hugo Lloris (Ph\u00e1p).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBa \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng sau l\u00e0 Chelsea, Man Utd v\u00e0 Man City v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng 7 c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t. C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u00e0 Liverpool (4), Leicester (2), Arsenal, Everton, Burnley, Stoke v\u00e0 West Brom (1).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec1u di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o khung 1h00 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 (11/7) v\u00e0 Croatia vs Anh (12/7).<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/croatia-vao-ban-ket-dejan-lovren-khen-dt-nga-465-190657.html\">Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Dejan Lovren b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khen \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/luka-modric-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-croatia-kich-tinh-nhu-phim-465-190652.html\">Luka Modric n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia: K\u1ecbch t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 phim</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-bi-troll-boi-rooney-va-beckham-sau-tran-thua-cua-thuy-dien-465-190650.html\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn, Ibrahimovic b\u1ecb troll v\u00ec l\u1ee1 d\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Beckham</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-mu-tuyen-anh-di-len-tu-tuyet-vong-thanh-tuyet-voi-421-190648.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU: Tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111i l\u00ean t\u1eeb tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng th\u00e0nh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lot-vao-ban-ket-nguoi-anh-bat-dau-mo-cup-vang-421-190647.html\">L\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u01a1 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-trong-ngay-anh-tro-lai-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-gan-ba-thap-ky-421-190646.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y Anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau g\u1ea7n ba th\u1eadp k\u1ef7?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4041","checkdouble":"190664"},{"date":"19:13 07/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 7/7: Ronaldo l\u00f4i k\u00e9o sao Real t\u1edbi Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/2/15/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-77-ronaldo-loi-keo-sao-real-toi-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 7/7.</h2><h2>Arsenal nh\u1eafm N&rsquo;Zonzi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Sky Sports, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i tho\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 N&rsquo;Zonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi The Gunners v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Premier League. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, N&rsquo;Zonzi \u0111ang c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng sau khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<h2>Paulinho c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Goal \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paulinho c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111ang t\u00ednh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u0169ng theo ngu\u1ed3n tin n\u00e0y, Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 Guangzhou Evergrande m\u01b0\u1ee3n Paulinho v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u0169ng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng anh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo l\u00f4i k\u00e9o Marcelo t\u1edbi Juventus\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 77 Ronaldo l\u00f4i k\u00e9o Marcelo t\u1edbi Juve h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 77 Ronaldo l\u00f4i k\u00e9o Marcelo t\u1edbi Juve h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/15/nhung-thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-tran-real-31-psg.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 7/7: Ronaldo l\u00f4i k\u00e9o Marcelo t\u1edbi Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Don Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Cristiano Ronaldo hy v\u1ecdng Marcelo s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng anh r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Real \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Juventus. Si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Turin theo m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro. V\u00e0 anh c\u0169ng mong mu\u1ed1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 Marcelo gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd.</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea cu\u1ed7m Jorginho t\u1eeb tay Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sport Italia, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng n\u1eabng tay tr\u00ean m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Jorginho c\u1ee7a Man City. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Jorginho v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Man xanh trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<h2>Klopp v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Mirror cho bi\u1ebft HLV Jurgen Klopp v\u1eabn \u0111ang s\u0103n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi mua Alisson v\u00e0 Jan Oblak nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1edf c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. V\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c d\u1ec5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<h2>Man City theo d\u00f5i Pavard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Suddeutsche Zeitung c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a tin Man City \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Benjamin Pavard c\u1ee7a Stuttgart. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay \u1edf World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 HLV Pep Guardiola hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bayern c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-0607-mu-muon-tao-ra-cu-soc-vu-ronaldo-184-190534.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 06/07: MU mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-67-ronaldo-gan-nhu-la-nguoi-cua-juve-184-190466.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 6/7: Ronaldo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4040","checkdouble":"190626"},{"date":"13:37 07/07","title":"Ng\u00f4i sao Neymar b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u c\u00f3 \u00edt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n s\u1ed1 ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/7/ngoi-sao-neymar-bi-che-gieu-co-it-ban-thang-hon-so-kieu-toc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n n\u00e0o trong g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9, Neymar nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1eef d\u1ed9i t\u1eeb m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i v\u00ec th\u00f3i quen \u0103n v\u1ea1 \u1edf World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9 t\u1ed1i 6/7, ng\u00f4i sao Neymar l\u00e0 m\u0169i d\u00f9i ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 khi anh c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 14 ph\u00fat n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n \u0103n v\u1ea1 k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup 2018. \u1ede cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Mexico v\u00f2ng 1/8, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00f2n l\u0103n l\u1ed9n, t\u1ecf v\u1ebb \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn, d\u00f9 Miguel Layun ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u1eb9 ch\u00e2n l\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9, Neymar tung ra ba c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o, v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Brazil v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n @AndreOwuor t\u1ecf v\u1ebb h\u1ea3 h\u00ea tr\u00ean Twitter: \"T\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft m\u00f9a World Cup c\u1ee7a Neymar\", k\u00e8m theo l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh ch\u1ee5p c\u1ea3nh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u0103n l\u1ed9n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/cc-7561-1530937218.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n @insoniascarvao vi\u1ebft: \"Ch\u00fac k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 t\u1ed1t l\u00e0nh, Neymar. H\u00e3y c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh nh\u00e9\". \u0110i c\u00f9ng l\u1eddi m\u1ec9a mai l\u00e0 b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p Neymar m\u1eb7c trang ph\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Brazil \u0111ang c\u01b0\u1ee1i s\u00f3ng bi\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n @AlexBenito1991 \u0111\u0103ng m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed9ng, gh\u00e9p c\u1ea3nh Neymar l\u0103n l\u1ed9n trong trang ph\u1ee5c \u00e1o thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Brazil tr\u00ean b\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n h\u00e0nh l\u00fd \u1edf s\u00e2n bay, k\u00e8m ch\u00fa th\u00edch: \"Ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng Neymar v\u00e0 Brazil \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n @wellywellard b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn: \"Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Milorad Mazic kh\u00f4ng r\u01a1i v\u00e0o c\u00e1i b\u1eaby \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil. Th\u1eadt x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn m\u00e0 l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o v\u00e0 kh\u00f3c l\u00f3c nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e1m con n\u00edt\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n @JaspreetSSahni \u0111\u01b0a th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd: \"\u0110\u1eebng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ebfn Kazan trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghe h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn vi\u00ean du l\u1ecbch gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u, r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ec5n c\u1ea3 \u0110\u1ee9c, Argentina v\u00e0 Brazil v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf World Cup 2018\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n @FIFAWC2018 m\u1ec9a mai Neymar: \"C\u00f3 ai nh\u1eadn ra, s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a anh ta c\u00f2n \u00edt h\u01a1n s\u1ed1 ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c kh\u00f4ng\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua B\u1ec9 1-2, Neymar \u0111\u1ee9ng im m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh, kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i l\u1eddi n\u00e0o, \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng. M\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Neymar, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Felipe Luis v\u00e0 Vincent Kompany, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng t\u1ecf c\u1ea3m x\u00fac g\u00ec.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4039","checkdouble":"190598"},{"date":"12:47 07/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 1-0 H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng (H2): V\u1eeba d\u1eabn b\u00e0n, v\u1eeba h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/da-nang-vs-hai-phong-vong-18-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng v\u00f2ng 18 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 7/7.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng v\u00f2ng 18 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 7/7.</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng clic